        This sample demonstrates the basic rendering of the <a href="https://www.syncfusion.com/aspnet-mvc-ui-controls/carousel" target="_blank" aria-label="ASP.NET MVC Carousel">ASP.NET MVC Carousel<span class="sr-only">opens in a new tab</span></a> component.
    </p>
}

